    "Models will naturally prioritize microbes and microbial genetic elements from well-studied environments and conditions (e.g., the human gut).",
    "On the other hand, current research has also demonstrated microbiome genome language models are capable of traversing genomic and protein spaces that are entirely unexplored by existing microbiome research.",
